);

const program = Effect.gen(function* () {
  const hb = yield* Effect.fork(heartbeat);
  yield* Effect.sleep("175 millis");
  yield* Fiber.interrupt(hb);
  yield* Console.log("stopped");
});

Effect.runPromise(program);
```

Interrupting the fibre stops the background loop cleanly — no dangling tasks.

